Package com.continuent.tungsten.replicator

Class Summary
ErrorNotification This class defines a ErrorNotification, which denotes a severe replication error that causes replication to fail.
InSequenceNotification This class defines a InSequenceNotification
OutOfSequenceNotification This class defines a OutOfSequenceException which is thrown if ReplicationEvent applier detects gap in transaction history sequence.
StateChangeNotification This class defines a StateChangeNotification
Version This class defines a Version
VersionManager This class defines methods to store ans retrieve module versions
 

Exception Summary
ReplicatorException This class defines a ReplicatorException, a parent for all other exceptions
